---
const metrics = [
  { value: "500+", label: "Clientes protegidos" },
  { value: "8+", label: "Anos de experiência" },
  { value: "50K+", label: "Câmeras monitoradas" },
  { value: "99.9%", label: "Uptime da central" },
];

const trustPoints = [
  "Equipe técnica certificada pelos principais fabricantes",
  "Central de monitoramento própria com redundância total",
  "Suporte técnico 24/7 com SLA de atendimento",
];
---

<section id="sobre" class="py-24 relative">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-fort-darker via-fort-dark/50 to-fort-darker"></div>
  <div class="section-divider absolute top-0 left-0 right-0"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <p class="text-blur-in text-fort-blue text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase mb-3">Sobre Nós</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-fort-white mb-4">
        <span class="text-slide-up block overflow-hidden"><span class="inner">Tecnologia e experiência a serviço da sua proteção</span></span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Left: Text + Metrics -->
      <div class="reveal-left">
        <p class="text-fort-light text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10">
          Somos uma empresa de segurança eletrônica com foco em tecnologia. Combinamos inteligência artificial e monitoramento profissional para proteger empresas e condomínios com o que há de mais avançado no mercado.
        </p>

        <!-- 2x2 Metrics grid -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 stagger-children">
          {metrics.map((metric) => (
            <div class="bg-fort-gray/20 border border-fort-border/40 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:border-fort-blue/20 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-[0_8px_40px_rgba(42,111,242,0.08)]">
              <p class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-fort-blue mb-1">{metric.value}</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-fort-text leading-snug">{metric.label}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Trust points -->
      <div class="reveal-right">
        <div class="bg-fort-gray/20 border border-fort-border/40 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-fort-blue/10 transition-colors duration-500">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-fort-white mb-7">Por que escolher a BATALION</h3>

          <ul class="space-y-5">
            {trustPoints.map((point, i) => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-fort-blue/10 border border-fort-blue/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-fort-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <p class="text-fort-light text-sm leading-relaxed">{point}</p>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>

          <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-fort-border/30 flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-fort-green animate-ping-slow"></span>
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-fort-green absolute"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="relative w-2 h-2">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-fort-green block"></span>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs text-fort-green font-mono">Central operacional 24/7</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
